title: Jim Carrey carries ex-girlfriend's coffin at Ireland funeral
text:
*Los Angeles:* A solemn Jim Carrey served as a pallbearer for his ex-girlfriend, Cathriona White, at her funeral in Ireland on Saturday.
*Jim Carrey. Pic/Santa Banta*
White, 30, died of an apparent suicide in Los Angeles on September 28. The Irish-born makeup artist had dated Carrey, 53, on and off since meeting in 2012 and ... Â»
